'''Janet Lewin''' was a Visual Effects Producer for [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']].<ref name="Special Effects">{{YouTube|video=1iAIOuCNc4E|text=Star Wars Episode III - Special Effects|channel=channel/UCzNpiGEr2QEsjOm9bV6T9vw|name=Chief Mouse|archivedate=20201111000826}}</ref>She is now the Senior Vice President of Lucasfilm Visual Effects and General Manager of Industrial Light & Magic. She has most notably contributed to or worked on [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|Revenge of the Sith]] and many recent projects such as [[Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens|The Force Awakens]], [[Rogue One: A Star Wars Story|Rogue One]], [[Star Wars: Episode VIII The Last Jedi|The Last Jedi]], [[Solo: A Star Wars Story|Solo]], [[Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker|The Rise of Skywalker]] and [[Star Wars: The Mandalorian]].

